{"id":28,"parent_id":0,"book_id":23525,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":28,"title":"Guide to the Friend","subtitle":"","short_title":"Guide to the Friend","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Guide to the",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],["h1","Possible Ideas for Family Home Evening"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f91","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.f91"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13aug48-guide-to-the-friend.jpg"}]],[".figure",["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],["p.para","Together, read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/quest-for-testimony.p1"},"“Quest for Testimony”"],"(pages 2–3). Fill a small cup with soil and plant a seed. Work together to care for the plant and watch it grow. It can be a reminder to nurture your testimony each day."]],["li",["span.label","2."],["p.para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/a-light-in-the-dark.p1"},"“A Light in the Dark”"],"(pages 4–6). As a family, discuss what you can do to help the missionaries in your area. Write letters or draw pictures to send to a missionary you know from your family, ward, or neighborhood."]],["li",["span.label","3."],["p.para","Use the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/heavenly-father-hears-and-answers-my-prayers.p1"},"Bringing Primary Home"],"lesson and activity to learn more about this month’s Primary theme (pages 42–43)."]],["li",["span.label","4."],["p.para","Study the scriptures together. Use the ideas from",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/family-scripture-fun.p1"},"“Family Scripture Fun”"],"(page 24) to help your family learn from what you read."]],["li",["span.label","5."],["p.para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p1"},"Elder Holland’s message"],"on page 27. Take turns sharing what you are grateful for. Use the activity,",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/08/for-older-kids/a-box-of-blessings.p1"},"“A Box of Blessings”"],"(page 46), to make gratitude journal boxes."]]]]],[".resources",[".moreInfo",[".title","Hidden CTR Ring"],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p9"},"Did you find the ring? Look on page 22!"]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p10"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"can be found on the Internet at",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend"},"lds.org/friend"],". To subscribe online, go to",["a",{"href":"http://store.lds.org"},"store.lds.org"],"."]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p11"},"To send us a letter, drawing, or poem, please fill out this form and include it with your submission. Please also include a school photo or high-quality snapshot. Submissions will not be returned and may be edited for length and clarity. Children whose work is submitted should be at least three years old."],["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p12"},["span.emphasis","Please send your submission to:"]],[".address",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Magazine"],[".address","50 E. North Temple St., Rm. 2432"],[".address","Salt Lake City, UT 84150-0024"],[".address",["span.emphasis","Or email:"],["a",{"href":"mailto:friend@ldschurch.org"},"friend@ldschurch.org"]],["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p17"},["span.emphasis","The following information and permission must be included:"]],["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p18"},"Full name____________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p19"},"Age__________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/friend/2013/08/guide-to-the-friend.p20"},"State/Province, Country______________________"],["p.para",{"id"